oracle.pgx.api.graphalteration

Interface GraphAlterationEmptyEdgeProviderBuilder

  • All Superinterfaces:
    GraphAlterationBuilder, GraphAlterationEmptyProviderBuilder

    public interface GraphAlterationEmptyEdgeProviderBuilder
extends GraphAlterationEmptyProviderBuilder
    Builder to describe a new empty edge provider to add in a graph as part of a graph alteration.

    21.4
